Text to Speech dependancy
-----------------------------
npm install react-native-tts --save
npm install @react-native-community/slider --save

Image Picker
-------------
npm install react-native-image-picker --save

Please add the following permissions in the AndroidManifest.xml
<uses-permission android:name="android.permission.CAMERA"/>
<uses-permission android:name="android.permission.WRITE_EXTERNAL_STORAGE"/>

Video 
--------
npm install --save react-native-video
npm install --save react-native-media-controls

Drop down Multiple selecter picker
------------------------------------
npm install react-native-multiple-select --save
npm install react-native-vector-icons --save
react-native link react-native-vector-icons

Slider image
------------
npm install react-native-image-gallery --save
